      "writtenOn": "2021-03-10T19:53:21Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Beacuse\n1. BB V1 api handler, seeing \"branch:master\", auto-upgrades it to refs/heads/master before populating Build.GitilesCommit proto.\n2. BB v2 *may* abort with INVALID ARGUMENT if GitilesCommit.ref doesn\u0027t start with \"refs/\".\n\nSince I\u0027m not sure about (2), I was asking.",
