      "writtenOn": "2021-03-10T19:55:29Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "So, I\u0027ve looked (2): doc says must start with `refs/`\n  https://source.chromium.org/chromium/infra/infra/+/master:go/src/go.chromium.org/luci/buildbucket/proto/common.proto;l\u003d159?q\u003dbuildbucket%20build%20proto%20gitilesCommit\u0026ss\u003dchromium\n\nand at least Python handle does require it:\nhttps://source.chromium.org/chromium/infra/infra/+/master:appengine/cr-buildbucket/validation.py;l\u003d92\n\nSo, I think scheduler need to upgrade branch to ref 😞",
